    "media:imagetext": "Welcome to the wonderful world of the\nNomads! This\n375-mph\nElectra is the luxurious flying \"Clubhouse\" for Michigan's round-\nthe-world, non-profit air travel club. Organized in 1965, the Nomads\nhave flown throughout the Western Hemisphere, Europe, and Hawaii.\nMembers enjoy low flight costs, group hotel rates and free airport\nparking along with in-flight camaraderie and\npassenger prop-jet plane. NOMADS, 9293 Middlebelt Road, Romulus,\nMichigan 48174.\nPLACE\nSTAMP\nHERE\n2015.1661081",
